00:50:51.870 --> 00:50:55.140 align:middle line:84%
There's only two independent
Lorentz invariants.

00:50:55.140 --> 00:50:56.550 align:middle line:84%
With momentum
conservation, there

00:50:56.550 --> 00:51:00.840 align:middle line:84%
