can be written as--

00:55:05.720 --> 00:55:08.600 align:middle line:90%
so first, these two pi forth.

00:55:08.600 --> 00:55:11.120 align:middle line:84%
And then you have two
factor of 2 pi cubed.

00:55:11.120 --> 00:55:12.980 align:middle line:90%
