00:55:32.450 --> 00:55:41.000 align:middle line:84%
prime minus square root
s times delta 3 k1 plus

00:55:41.000 --> 00:55:48.950 align:middle line:90%
k2 and the d3 k1 and d3 k2.

00:55:48.950 --> 00:55:53.210 align:middle line:84%
So as we said, the k3, they
have to be equal and opposite

00:55:53.210 --> 00:55:53.795 align:middle line:90%
