00:55:53.795 --> 00:55:56.340 align:middle line:90%


00:55:56.340 --> 00:55:58.880 align:middle line:84%
And then you can just
evaluate one delta function.

00:55:58.880 --> 00:56:01.550 align:middle line:84%
And then the other
dk will remain.

00:56:01.550 --> 00:56:04.960 align:middle line:90%
The other dk will remain.

00:56:04.960 --> 00:56:08.590 align:middle line:90%
So essentially, you just have--

00:56:08.590 --> 00:56:11.220 align:middle line:84%
essentially, we can
