explain a little bit.

01:04:00.690 --> 01:04:03.815 align:middle line:84%
Again, this dP alpha
beta, we always mean--

01:04:03.815 --> 01:04:09.400 align:middle line:90%


01:04:09.400 --> 01:04:15.280 align:middle line:84%
