the decay around k2, et cetera,

01:04:58.020 --> 01:05:01.580 align:middle line:90%
and decay n around kn.

01:05:01.580 --> 01:05:06.050 align:middle line:84%
So when we write d alpha
beta, you should imagine this.

01:05:06.050 --> 01:05:07.220 align:middle line:90%
We already include that.

